gomodel:SYNGO_2408  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Overexpression of PTPRO increases the synapse density in cultured hippocampal neurons.\nKD of PTPRO by shRNA decreases the glutamatergic and GABAergic synaptic strength.. Experimental description: Materials and Methods\nNeuronal culture and artificial synapse formation\nCultured neurons were obtained from C57BL/6J mouse hippocampal cells.\n\nThrer is no information about the species for PTPRO expressing plasmid." ;
